sentences.english: Self-publishing these days is increasingly a tale of two cities.
sentences.chinese: 今自助出版越來越呈現兩極分化的趨勢。

sentences.english: And do Western welfare states have to be quite so buffet-like?
sentences.chinese: 還有，西方福利社會一定要像個自助餐一樣無度嗎？

sentences.english: The website will also have a section to encourage people to submit their own writings.
sentences.chinese: 網站中包含一個自助欄目，鼓勵用戶提交自己的作品。

sentences.english: Self-Serve Debit And Credit Card Only.

sentences.english: There's a cafeteria on the ground floor.

sentences.english: The teachers could manage the information on ATW by themselves.
sentences.chinese: 教師可通過後臺管理系統自主自助維護信息內容。

sentences.english: The application must have some level of self-service sign-up.
sentences.chinese: 應用程序必須具備某種程度的自助註冊功能。

sentences.english: Please take away those salad bars, For they all overlook . The fact that I go out to eat.

sentences.english: The dorms are all equipped with launderettes and hot water is available 24 hours a day.
sentences.chinese: 樓內設有自助式洗衣機，24小時供應熱水等。

sentences.english: And we enter an upward spiral between self-help and other-help.

sentences.english: Organization is receiving the funding support from SWD for self-help organizations of PWDs.
sentences.chinese: 機構現時有接受社署給予殘疾人士自助組織的資助。

sentences.english: Dormitory parents and cafeteria workers receive paychecks from the school.
sentences.chinese: 宿舍的舍長和自助食堂的工人從學校領到了工資。

sentences.english: In fact, god will help you only after your self-help.
sentences.chinese: 其實，人必自助然後纔有天助。
